    <item>
      <title>学校称，ICE 特工在哥伦比亚大楼内逮捕学生</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/26/nyregion/columbia-university-ice-student.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据该大学称，联邦官员谎报了自己以获得访问权限。市长佐兰·马姆达尼 (Zohran Mamdani) 表示，特朗普总统告诉他，这名学生将“立即被释放”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/26/nyregion/columbia-university-ice-student.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 20:42:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹佛市长禁止 ICE 进入城市财产并下令保护抗议者</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/26/us/denver-mayor-ice-defiance.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市长迈克·约翰斯顿（Mike Johnston）的命令是对他谨慎立场的挑衅性转变，在特朗普总统在竞选期间承诺在那里发生“血腥故事”后，可能会引起人们对大丹佛的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/26/us/denver-mayor-ice-defiance.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 20:24:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
